description: Lists all your signing jobs. You can use the maxResults parameter to limit the number of signing jobs that are returned in the response. If additional jobs remain to be listed, AWS Signer returns a nextToken value. Use this value in subsequent calls to ListSigningJobs to fetch the remaining values. You can continue calling ListSigningJobs with your maxResults parameter and with new values that Signer returns in the nextToken parameter until all of your signing jobs have been returned.

nested_items.name: jobs
nested_items.description: A list of your signing jobs.

nested_items.name: jobId
nested_items.description: The ID of the signing job.

nested_items.name: bucketName
nested_items.description: Name of the S3 bucket.

nested_items.name: key
nested_items.description: Key name of the bucket object that contains your unsigned code.

nested_items.name: version
nested_items.description: Version of your source image in your version enabled S3 bucket.

nested_items.name: signedObject
nested_items.description: A SignedObject structure that contains information about a signing job's signed code image.

nested_items.name: bucketName
nested_items.description: Name of the S3 bucket.

nested_items.name: key
nested_items.description: Key name that uniquely identifies a signed code image in your bucket.

nested_items.name: signingMaterial
nested_items.description: A SigningMaterial object that contains the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the certificate used for the signing job.

nested_items.name: certificateArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the certificates that is used to sign your code.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the signing job was created.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the signing job.

nested_items.name: isRevoked
nested_items.description: Indicates whether the signing job is revoked.

nested_items.name: profileName
nested_items.description: The name of the signing profile that created a signing job.

nested_items.name: profileVersion
nested_items.description: The version of the signing profile that created a signing job.

nested_items.name: platformId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for a signing platform.

nested_items.name: platformDisplayName
nested_items.description: The name of a signing platform.

nested_items.name: signatureExpiresAt
nested_items.description: The time when the signature of a signing job expires.

nested_items.name: jobOwner
nested_items.description: The AWS account ID of the job owner.

nested_items.name: jobInvoker
nested_items.description: The AWS account ID of the job invoker.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: String for specifying the next set of paginated results.
